{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>SmileDirectClub doesn&#8217;t require any in-person office visits and is up to 60% less than traditional braces. Our aligners straighten teeth under the supervision of a network of <a href=\"https:\/\/blogorigin.wpengine.com\/doctors-behind-your-smile\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">250 affiliated, state licensed dentists and orthodontists<\/a>. Plus,\u00a0our aligners are\u00a0a great option for\u00a0servicemen and\u00a0servicewomen\u00a0because they&#8217;re approved for\u00a0deployment. (We also offer an active military discount, among several other benefits.)<span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Just in time for the\u00a04th\u00a0of July,\u00a0Elijah and Sierra are sharing why\u00a0SmileDirectClub\u00a0was the best choice for their family \u2013 and how they&#8217;ll be celebrating our country&#8217;s independence this year together as a family.<span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_1582\" style=\"width: 360px\" class=\"wp-caption alignright\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1582\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-1582\" src=\"https:\/\/blogorigin.wpengine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/military-family-smiledirectclub-elijah-redmond.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"350\" height=\"489\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blogorigin.wpengine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/military-family-smiledirectclub-elijah-redmond.png 788w, https:\/\/blogorigin.wpengine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/military-family-smiledirectclub-elijah-redmond-215x300.png 215w, https:\/\/blogorigin.wpengine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/military-family-smiledirectclub-elijah-redmond-768x1072.png 768w, https:\/\/blogorigin.wpengine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/milita